<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="active-adj">active <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'æktɪv/    美 /ˈæktɪv/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(行动、思想) 活跃的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 inactive </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a child with a very active imagination 
想象力很丰富的孩子</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Being an active young person, I like sports and outdoor activities.
作为一个活跃的年轻人，我喜欢体育运动和户外活动。</p><footer>2011 辽宁书面表达</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>积极 (参与) 的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Encourage students to <strong>take an active part in</strong> discussions.
鼓励学生积极参与讨论。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You should <strong>take active steps</strong> to make your dreams come true.
你应该积极采取行动，实现自己的梦想。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>be active in (doing) sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She has been active in local education for many years.
多年来，她一直积极参与当地的教育事业。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>起作用的；(火山等) 活的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>medicine that is active against cold 
抗感冒药</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an <strong>active volcano</strong> 
活火山</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>[语法] 主动的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 passive </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>“Tom told me.” is an active sentence, and “I was told by Tom.” is passive.
“汤姆告诉我。”是主动句，“我被汤姆告知。”是被动句。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>While a person is asleep, a part of his brain is still <strong><em>_</em></strong>__(活跃的).  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. active  </p></div>